    "body": "You can use `webContents.capturePage` to take screenshots of part or all of the page.\n\nSee http://electron.atom.io/docs/api/web-contents/#contentscapturepagerect-callback for more details.\n\nYou can also use the `desktopCapturer` APIs to take screenshots outside of the current window, http://electron.atom.io/docs/api/desktop-capturer/\n\nClosing this out.\n"
