    "updated_at": "2017-02-04T03:44:18Z",
    "body": "I do have the similar issue as @abnerlee mentioned above. I have tried to pass the `Rectangle` obj into the `capturePage` method but it seems only changing the output image size instead of changing the bound of the screenshot.\r\n\r\n```js\r\n            const remote = require('electron').remote;\r\n            const webContents = remote.getCurrentWebContents();\r\n\r\n            webContents.capturePage({\r\n                x: 0,\r\n                y: 0,\r\n                width: 1000,\r\n                height: 2000\r\n            }, (img) => {\r\n                remote.require('fs')\r\n                    .writeFile(TEMP_URL, img.toPng());\r\n            });\r\n```\r\n"
